Package: pixelpack
Architecture: amd64
Description: Pillow-based image-processing CLI
 Pixelpack is a small command-line tool for common image operations:
 resizing, format conversion, and grayscale conversion. It is distributed
 as a standalone binary compiled with Nuitka.
